mapper.select:
select `order`.order_code, `order`.sum_price, `order`.order_status, `order`.cus_code, `user`.user_name, `user`.phone, `order`.version from t_sys_order `order` left join t_sys_user `user` on (`order`.cus_code = `user`.user_code and `user`.is_delete = 0) where `order`.is_delete = 0 and `order`.store_code = #{storeCode}
AND `order`.order_status = #{orderStatus}
order by `order`.create_time desc
